
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Sticky Mobile Safe</title>

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
}

body{
font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
background:black; /* evita flash blanco */
}

/* sección de scroll */

.scroll-section{
height:300vh;
position:relative;
}

/* sticky */

.sticky{
position:sticky;
top:0;
height:100vh;
overflow:hidden;

display:flex;
align-items:center;
justify-content:center;

transform:translateZ(0);
will-change:transform;
}

/* imagen más grande que viewport */

.sticky img{
width:100%;
height:120vh;
object-fit:cover;
}

/* contenido después */

.content{
padding:120px 10%;
font-size:22px;
line-height:1.6;
background:white;
}

.content:nth-child(even){
background:#f3f3f3;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<section class="scroll-section">

<div class="sticky">
<img src="https://picsum.photos/1920/1080">
</div>

</section>

<section class="content">
<h2>Bloque de texto 1</h2>
<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore.</p>
</section>

<section class="content">
<h2>Bloque de texto 2</h2>
<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore.</p>
</section>

<section class="content">
<h2>Bloque de texto 3</h2>
<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore.</p>
</section>

</body>
</html>
